<template>
    <!-- Header-->
    <HeaderPage />
    <!-- AllBroducts-->
    <AllProducts
        v-for="post in posts"
        :key="post.id"
        :id="post.id"
        :userId="post.userId"
        :title="post.title"
        :body="post.body"
    />/>
    <!-- OtherCompany-->

    <OtherCompany />
    <!-- FooTer -->

    <FooTer />

    <router-view />
</template>

<script>
// @ is an alias to /src
import HeaderPage from "@/components/Header.vue";
import AllProducts from "@/components/AllProducts.vue";
import FooTer from "@/components/footer.vue";
import OtherCompany from "@/components/OtherCompany.vue";
import jsonpost from "../json/post.json";

export default {
    components: {
        HeaderPage,
        AllProducts,
        OtherCompany,
        FooTer,
    },
    data: function () {
        return {
            posts: jsonpost,
        };
    },
};
</script>
<style></style>
